---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy-800">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Heading -->
    <h2 data-aos="fade-up" class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-16">
      The People Behind the Lens
    </h2>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Aldrian -->
      <div data-aos="fade-right" class="bg-navy-700 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-navy-900 border-2 border-silver-300/20">
          <img
            src="/images/aldrian.jpg"
            alt="Aldrian Francis"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Aldrian Francis</h3>
        <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Lead Photographer</p>
        <p class="text-silver-300 leading-relaxed">
          With an eye for dramatic light and bold compositions, Aldrian brings stories to life through every frame.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Jillian -->
      <div data-aos="fade-left" class="bg-navy-700 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-navy-900 border-2 border-silver-300/20">
          <img
            src="/images/jillian.jpg"
            alt="Jillian Grace"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            onerror="this.style.display='none'"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Jillian Grace</h3>
        <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Creative Photographer</p>
        <p class="text-silver-300 leading-relaxed">
          Jillian's warm and candid style captures the genuine emotions that make every moment unforgettable.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Shared line -->
    <p data-aos="fade-up" class="text-center text-silver-300 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Together, we are <span class="text-white font-semibold">A.F. Photography</span> — two siblings with one lens, chasing the perfect shot across the Philippines.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
